

# Handoff Document: Gemini Web UI Session Logger — Chrome Extension

## Project Codename: LVS_Gemini

---

## 1. Project Purpose

A Chrome Manifest V3 extension that **passively captures** Gemini web app interactions where **both** an image input **and** a text prompt are present. No automation — all input remains manual. The extension intercepts network traffic, extracts structured data, and persists it to a local SQLite3 database with associated image files on disk.

---

## 2. Trigger Condition

The extension **only fires** when a Gemini interaction contains:

- ✅ At least one uploaded image **AND** text prompt
- ❌ Text-only prompts → ignored
- ❌ Image-only without text → ignored

---

## 3. Target Environment

| Parameter | Value |
