## 8. Data Extraction Map — What to Intercept

| Data Point | Source | Key/Location |
|---|---|---|
| **Prompt text** | StreamGenerate chunk with key `"11"` | `"11":["{text}"]` |
| **Thinking mode flag** | Presence of chunk with `"Show Thinking"` | Key `"7"`, index `` |
| **Thinking text** | Main payload chunk, Format A string | Inside `file_content_fetcher_tool` response |
| **Input image filename** | Main payload chunk | `"0b62bc10fa6e61a6_DSC_0428.jpg"` — strip prefix before first `_` |
| **Input image URL** | Main payload chunk | `lh3.googleusercontent.com/gg/...` |
| **Input image metadata** | Main payload chunk | `[width, height, filesize]` = `[1024, 682, 196182]` |
| **Output image URLs** | Main payload chunk + separate fetches | `lh3.googleusercontent.com/gg-dl/AOI_d_...` |
| **Output image metadata** | Main payload chunk | `[1264, 842, 1201186]` per image |
| **Conversation ID** | Every chunk after first | `"c_109e00563eac533e"` |
| **Response ID** | First chunk | `"r_67d33de905ac70d7"` |
| **Candidate ID** | Main payload chunk | `"rc_5c93b88e55a41b35"` |
| **Model label** | Thinking toggle chunk or final payload | `"Nano Banana 2"` |
| **Image gen ID** | Request header `x-goog-ext-525001261-jspb` and response payload | `"e051ce1aa80aa576"` |
| **Synthetic prompt** | Main payload chunk | Long English string with `<IMAGE_0>` reference |
| **Response text** | Main payload chunk, candidate content | First element of candidate `parts` — `[""]` for image-only |

