## 9. File System Layout

```
Desktop/
  LVS_Gemini/
    gemini_logs.db              ← SQLite3 database
    input/
      {id}_128px.png            ← 128px downscaled input image
    output/
      {id}_0_preview.png        ← Auto-captured output preview
      {id}_1_preview.png        ← (if multiple candidates)
```

- Input images are **always** stored as 128px thumbnails (longest edge = 128px, aspect preserved)
- Output previews are captured at whatever resolution `AOI_d_` serves (typically ~1024px)
- When user manually saves full-size and reconciles → preview is **deleted**, `output_fullsize_saved` flips to `1`
- Unsaved outputs (previews still present, `output_fullsize_saved = 0`) = **failed/rejected generation**

